  utils:::format.object_size("auto")
## [1] "37.1 Kb"
file.info("../data/challenge.rds")$size %>%
  utils:::format.object_size("auto")
## [1] "31.9 Kb"

haven

library(haven)

# SAS
read_sas(system.file("examples", "iris.sas7bdat", package = "haven"))
## # A tibble: 150 x 5
##    Sepal_Length Sepal_Width Petal_Length Petal_Width Species
